# ── Vendored DefraDB binary (DefraSync experiment) ──────────────
# 173 MB upstream release — never committed; fetched per-machine via Tools/defradb/fetch.sh.
# The script + checksum file are committed so both Macs land on the same pinned version.
Tools/defradb/defradb-darwin-*

# ── Python bytecode (tools/linux-capture) ─────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc
